window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Kingdom of Delain is at stake when King Roland is murdered and his son and rightful heir, Peter, is framed for the crime. Plotting against him is the evil Flagg and his pawn, young Prince Thomas. Yet with every plan there are holes - like Thomas's terrible secret. And the determined Prince Peter, who is planning a daring escape from his imprisonment. </p> <p>Stephen King has taken the classic fairy tale and transformed it into a masterpiece of fiction for the ages. </p>"; 
